<div class="Div5">
  <div class="right" id="Links"></div>
<h1 style="color: rgba(201, 13, 13, 0.89);">Links</h1>

<p>In a website, a hyperlink (or link) is an item like a word or button that points to another location. When you click on a link, the link will take you to the target of the link, which may be a webpage, document or other online content. Websites use hyperlinks as a way to navigate online content. Example Below:</p>
<h3><b><a href="https://youtu.be/sPnAJdsPHeQ?list=RDfs2g1cO3v7Y" target="_blank">This is a link</a></b></h3>
