<div class="Div8">
<h1 style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Website Layout</h1>
<p>A website layout is the arrangement of all visual elements on a webpage. Through the intentional positioning of page elements, we can control the relationship between them to better guide the user experience.</p>
